{"tid":836684,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"正宗嘅茶走","createTime":"2018-09-25T23:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T10:28:05.000Z","uid":14175,"like":269,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b8d6315ecb8e12f49600ea2d794d3d45f4816a0c","tid":836684,"uid":14175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T23:13:13.000Z","msg":"喺我嘅認知當中<br />\n一杯茶走嘅沖法應該係茶低再加練奶<br />\n一滴花奶都唔應該存在<br />\n但眼見而家好多餐廳<br />\n叫佢地嘅茶走都係落咗花奶<br />\n一問之下佢地話練奶係當糖嘅作用<br />\n但由細到大茶走都係取代花奶同糖<br />\n唔知由幾時開始出面嘅餐廳重新定義茶走<br />\n真係想問下大家一杯茶酒應該係點嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該係茶底加練奶<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 茶走要加埋花奶先岩"},{"pid":"8ddb323a42c995536d892a16d5673d26efd4fee7","tid":836684,"uid":32706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T23:22:44.000Z","msg":"茶加煉奶"},{"pid":"a3d52c0c43b847540c33d510ed2767fa7f236cbf","tid":836684,"uid":200641,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T23:35:03.000Z","msg":"係用用煉奶代替花奶<br />\n令到杯奶茶入口滑啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad9ea520a5980eb9e4c87c014a618d742231c18","tid":836684,"uid":36691,"like":3,"dislike":26,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T23:36:24.000Z","msg":"淨用煉奶杯野咪甜到仆街<br />\n落得少又冇奶味"},{"pid":"17df73c658d8cc46d3e76124c00a6b47504d2bf6","tid":836684,"uid":27416,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T23:44:21.000Z","msg":"淨煉奶太多會甜<br />\n太少會唔夠色"},{"pid":"2b178013fbc70c69a46ee0f8260a50d54c93a457","tid":836684,"uid":31200,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T23:49:22.000Z","msg":"大快活會比個茶底你自己落煉奶lol"},{"pid":"5b8e24e6e657fd7f88f74afeb71a0647a47c844e","tid":836684,"uid":14175,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:43:02.000Z","msg":"但有人因為腸胃對花奶敏感<br />\n所以諗住飲茶走<br />\n點知都係有花奶<br />\n結果又係肚痾"},{"pid":"98b61793b6f3e337ce0b0a14f0441b489aded63f","tid":83668